Class RestaurantHours

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.mainapplication.datainterface.DataClasses.RestaurantHours
  • public class RestaurantHours
extends java.lang.Object
    The RestaurantHours class is a data class that holds the hours of a restaurant. It is used to store the hours of a restaurant for the day It contains a list of RestaurantHour objects - RestaurantHour is a data class that holds the hours of a restaurant for a specific section

    Ryan Leska
